Monitoring Servers with Prometheus & Grafana


Head over to the Graph tab in your Prometheus UI (http://localhost:9090) and try pasting these to see your system's health:

### 1. Common Metrics to Query
CPU Usage (Percentage):

`100 - (avg by (instance) (rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode="idle"}[5m])) * 100)`

### 2. Memory Usage (Percent%):
`node_memory_Active_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes * 100`
### 3. Disk Space Available (GB):

Code snippet
node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint="/"} / 1024 / 1024 / 1024
